  "detailed_description": "\"Aim Theory - Trainer\" is the scientific way to improve your aiming skills for FPS games.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- More than 7 training levels that make your skill more accurate and fast.<br />\r\n- You can adjust the difficulty of the levels with precision.<br />\r\n- You can adjust the field of view(FOV) in 3 different modes. (Vertical FOV, Horizontal FOV, 4:3 Horizontal HOV)<br />\r\n- You can adjust mouse sensitivity with the value as in  Overwatch or Counter strike.",
  "about_the_game": "\"Aim Theory - Trainer\" is the scientific way to improve your aiming skills for FPS games.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- More than 7 training levels that make your skill more accurate and fast.<br />\r\n- You can adjust the difficulty of the levels with precision.<br />\r\n- You can adjust the field of view(FOV) in 3 different modes. (Vertical FOV, Horizontal FOV, 4:3 Horizontal HOV)<br />\r\n- You can adjust mouse sensitivity with the value as in  Overwatch or Counter strike.",
